"""Return the send, receive value to initialize a KIM101 unit."""
stdin = ThorLabsPacket(message_id=ThorLabsCommands.HW_REQ_INFO, param1=0,

    source=80, data=hw_info_data.pack(b'\x01\x02\x03\x04', 'KIM101'.encode(
